data.description: Charming 4 bedroom ranch in highly sought after subdivision in South PTC. Bright spacious open plan with separate great room with lovely fireplace, separate dining room, large kitchen with quartz countertops and new stainless appliances, breakfast bar and breakfast room. An additional sun room with views of the partially wooded back yard. Master suite is situated to the rear of the house for extra privacy, featuring trey ceiling, his and her vanities, separate shower and soaking bath. 2 more large bedrooms on the main level, with a double vanity bathroom and laundry room with a sink. Bonus bedroom upstairs with large bathroom. Loads of walk in attic storage. Fenced backyard. Newer roof and gutters. Two car garage with openers. Starr's Mill school district.
